parameters:
\nw[\N[21]]There seems to be a magical energy response
nearby.

\nw[\N[3]]Judging from the wind and sound, it seems like
we're reaching a dead end soon.

\nw[\N[21]]I see... Can you determine the number through
reconnaissance?
\nw[\N[3]]I can't tell, can you figure it out, Uka?
\nw[Uka]Hmm... What could it be?
\nw[\N[21]]Are you sure?

\nw[Uka]What on earth... is there... if it's hiding...
it's a mystery...

\nw[\N[21]]Hmmm... There might be a way to sneak through the
reconnaissance. It would be easier if there's only
one...

\nw[\N[21]]Let's head towards the direction where the
monsters are for now.
\nw[Uka]Oh......
A

\nw[\N[21]]There's a monster... The magical tool also
indicates that it's the target monster...
\nw[\N[21]]Is that what Uka's search detected?
\nw[Uka]......Yeah......that's right......

\nw[Uka]......But...this monster here...seems different,
doesn't it?
\nw[\N[21]]What do you mean it's different?
\nw[Uka]......Um......the atmosphere?

\nw[\N[21]]Atmosphere... come to think of it, the monsters
here were watery, but that one seems like a
monster with a strong wind attribute.

\nw[\N[21]]Wind monsters are often weak to fire attribute, so
let's consider that and prepare.

\nw[\N[21]]One person should stay on guard for ambushes and
surprise attacks, while the rest of the team
defeats that monster.

\nw[Huma]Alright~ I have to show them a place that seems
like a senpai~
\nw[\N[21]]Let's go into battle once we're prepared.
\nw[Uka]Oh...
A
\nw[\N[21]]Well, shall we fight the monsters...
Fight
Prepare
\nw[\N[21]]Alright, let's go!
!Flame
!Flame

\nw[\N[21]]Did we defeat them...? I guess it's because they
were absorbing magic, the magic reaction has
disappeared.

\nw[\N[21]]I'll just report to Prae since I can contact her.
Well, it's only when Prae is looking at me
though...
\nw[Uka]\N[3]... this...
\nw[\N[3]]What's wrong?
\nw[\N[3]]Um... is this the drop from the monster?
\nw[Uka]It was attached to the monster's chest...
\nw[\N[3]]Is this... a type of magical device?
\nw[\N[21]]Hm? A magical device?
\nw[\N[3]]Did you finish contacting [Char_9]?

\nw[\N[21]]No, not yet... but it seems Prae can see this side
too, so show me a little.
\nw[\N[3]]Yes, this is it.
\nw[\N[21]]Thank goodness, it seems you can see me. Um...?

\nw[\N[21]]It seems like it's some kind of magic used when
commanding familiars. It looks like a magical
tool, but it seems to be just regular magic.

\nw[\N[21]]It said that it would disappear as soon as the
monster died... and while I was saying that, it
disappeared.

\nw[\N[3]]Familiars... so there really is someone
controlling them.

\nw[\N[21]]It seems so. Maybe it was sucking the magic power
from this monster and then stealing it even more.

\nw[\N[3]]So, if it's called a familiar, that means it's
stronger than this. And it might realize that it
was defeated.

\nw[\N[3]]I think we should retreat early. This monster was
strong, and now that we've defeated its familiar,
we can't avoid becoming enemies.

\nw[\N[21]]......Yeah, it's more likely that it was just a
coincidence that Rodrigo happened to be the one
who accidentally absorbed the magic power, rather
than intentionally choosing him to do so.

\nw[\N[21]]Moreover, we can't expect any reinforcements here.
Our objective has been achieved, so let's quickly
return to the carriage and go back to town.
\nw[Uka]Oh...
\nw[\N[21]]Let's prepare a little more.
